<doxygen xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="compound.xsd" version="1.14.0" xml:lang="en-US">
  <compounddef id="TICKS" kind="page">
    <compoundname>TICKS</compoundname>
    <title>TICKS Function</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">TICKS</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Returns the system <bold>uptime in milliseconds</bold>.</para>
<para>The value represents how long the system has been running since it was started, with finer precision than <ref refid="UPSECS" kindref="compound">UPSECS</ref>.</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<sect1 id="TICKS_1examples-74_1s1"><sect2 id="TICKS_1examples-74_1s2"><sect3 id="TICKS_1examples-74">
<title>Examples</title><para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">REM<sp/>Print<sp/>uptime<sp/>in<sp/>milliseconds</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;Uptime<sp/>(ms):<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>TICKS</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">REM<sp/>Measure<sp/>how<sp/>long<sp/>something<sp/>takes</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">START<sp/>=<sp/>TICKS</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PROCdostuff()<sp/>&apos;<sp/>...<sp/>do<sp/>something<sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ELAPSED<sp/>=<sp/>TICKS<sp/>-<sp/>START</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;Elapsed<sp/>time:<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>ELAPSED;<sp/>&quot;<sp/>ms&quot;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">REM<sp/>Simple<sp/>delay<sp/>loop</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">START<sp/>=<sp/>TICKS</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">WHILE<sp/>TICKS<sp/>-<sp/>START<sp/>&lt;<sp/>1000</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ENDWHILE</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;1<sp/>second<sp/>has<sp/>passed&quot;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
</sect3></sect2></sect1>
<sect1 id="TICKS_1notes-72_1s1"><sect2 id="TICKS_1notes-72_1s2"><sect3 id="TICKS_1notes-72">
<title>Notes</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Returns a steadily increasing integer value starting from <bold>0</bold> at system boot.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Resolution is <bold>milliseconds</bold>, suitable for more precise timing than seconds.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Ideal for profiling, animation timing, and short delays.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ref refid="UPSECS" kindref="compound">UPSECS</ref> · <ref refid="SLEEP" kindref="compound">SLEEP</ref> </para>
</sect3></sect2></sect1>
    </detaileddescription>
